01:26:33,520 --> 01:26:33,920
Oh, dobro.

161
01:26:34,880 --> 01:26:36,960
Prije nego što dođemo do pitanja publike.

162
01:28:30,000 --> 01:28:35,440
Kad shadow aspekti pokazuju, ne znamo da su to shadow aspekti jer su u subconsciousu.

163
01:28:35,520 --> 01:28:37,200
Mislim, očito, nećete znati.

164
01:28:37,840 --> 01:28:41,360
The only way you know is koga upoznate na road.

165
01:28:42,240 --> 01:28:46,320
Do you have continual problems s jednom određenom tipom osobe?

166
01:28:46,640 --> 01:28:51,600
Do you have a repetitive pattern of situacije arising in your life that challenge you?

167
01:28:52,320 --> 01:28:55,200
Do you keep stumbling over the same blocks?

168
01:28:56,560 --> 01:29:02,560
These aspekti pokušavaju vam pokazati da su to vaša shadow, which is why I said earlier, just imagine a mirror.

169
01:29:03,680 --> 01:29:07,840
Because everything that happens to you is a reflection of who you believe yourself to be.

170
01:30:24,240 --> 01:30:31,120
Line, ljudi's names, whatever, write on piece papira i stavite ih u envelope.

171
01:30:31,520 --> 01:30:34,080
Ne stavljajte svoje najgore noćne more u nju.

172
01:30:34,720 --> 01:30:37,360
To je recept za disaster, a vi ćete se depresivno.

173
01:30:38,000 --> 01:30:45,440
Stavite slike sunca u nju, stavite slike hummingbirda i butterflies i flowers, ne samo horor priče.

174
01:30:45,600 --> 01:30:48,880
Tako ćete dobiti miks informacija u folderu.

175
01:30:49,040 --> 01:30:49,760
U redu?

176
01:30:50,400 --> 01:30:54,880
Kao što ste prošli taj folder at home i vi prolazite kroz njega i razmišljate, oh, hang on a moment, što je?

177
01:30:54,960 --> 01:30:58,320
Uzmite jednu at random i pogledajte je.

178
01:30:58,880 --> 01:30:59,360
Jedna slika.

179
01:31:00,000 --> 01:31:01,680
To bi bio ime osobe, bilo što.

180
01:31:40,320 --> 01:31:43,440
Kompleksno u mnogim aspektima, ali u nekim je aspektima vrlo jednostavno.

181
01:31:44,080 --> 01:31:45,840
Dakle, kada je sljedeći radionica u Hrvatskoj?

182
01:31:45,920 --> 01:31:46,880
U Hrvatskoj, u listopadu.

183
01:31:46,960 --> 01:31:47,920
Samo je vikend na svemirskom putovanju.

184
01:31:48,160 --> 01:31:48,560
O, oprosti.

185
01:31:48,640 --> 01:31:48,880
18.

